{
  "stem": "18626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only good thing-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only good time was if you got a extra loaf of bread by mistake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Or you got a piece of butter in trading with a Gentile person who gave you, you know, like a kilo of butter for a fancy golden ring.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because a lot of times, you traded with them and you were not lucky because it had to be a fast trade.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Guards were all the time watching you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it had to be traded fast outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one time, my mother gave a woman-- she was walking my mother outside of the ghetto in a factory where they were slaughtering chickens for the German army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And an old lady-- which I hate to say, with a big cross too-- was trading with my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother gave her a ring, and it was in the wintertime, very cold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the woman gave her in a paper, wrapped up, a big piece of butter, supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Mother was happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wow, she got for that little ring a nice big piece of butter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when she came home and we opened up the paper and we cut it in was a big stone inside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The butter was only smeared around the stone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German woman got away with the ring, and we got just a thin covering on a stone with butter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was done by a Gentile Lithuanian old lady with a cross.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother kept her wedding ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would never give out that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two things in the crematorium she had to give up is my little brother, and the ring was pulled off before she went to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
